caption.center: PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. WALEED

opinion.opinion_text:
On order of the Court, the delayed application for leave to appeal from the August 10, 1998 decision of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
Corrigan, J., not participating.
